transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan ji sir, wo jo temporary pacemaker jo company de raha hai, unka thoda contact number bhejiye na.
Executive: Kinka sir?
Customer: Temporary pacemaker wo heart patient wala jo lagta hai na heart patient ko.
Executive: Aap kaun baat kar rahe hain sir?
Customer: Main ek company se baat kar raha hu, Steel Brother mera company ka naam hai.
Executive: Steel Brother?
Customer: Steel Brother.
Executive: Ji Steel Brother.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Okay, okay, okay. Kinka contact number chahiye sir aapko batayenge?
Customer: Temporary pacemaker.
Executive: Ek minute, matlab ye kya buyer hai aapke sir? Baat hui hai kya aapki inse?
Customer: Nahi, nahi, nahi. Humko contact number chahiye.
Executive: Aapko chahiye contact number? Wo jo Delhi se jo sab bechte hai na medical item uske sath mein temporary pacemaker bhi bechte hai koi koi.
Executive: Accha.
Executive: Main samajh nahi pa rahi ab wo waha unka number kaise main kaise nikal paungi sir batayenge aap? 
Customer: Heart heart patient ko jo heart patient ka koi aapke paas add diya hua hai waha pe?
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Uska usme rahega temporary pacemaker TMPT.
Executive: TMPT?
Customer: Haan temporary pacemaker M.
Executive: Sir pura spelling bata do mujhe. TEM temporary.
Executive: Temporary.
Customer: Haan press maker.
Executive: Press maker.
Customer: Hmm. Is naam se koi company nahi aa rahi sir hamare paas to.
Customer: Us naam pe company kyu rahega ji, us naam se wo to ek item hai uska naam hai wo saman ka naam hai temporary pacemaker uska wo kaise rahega?
Executive: Accha accha okay aapko buyer ka chahiye na contact number?
Customer: Haan buyer ka chahiye haan.
Executive: Are to aisa bolo sir aapne to mujhe confuse hi kar diya.
Customer: Waisa hi to bol raha hu main.
Executive: Accha accha ruk jao ruk jao main kar rahi hu. Aap hi ka product hai na ye aapke catalog mein bhi hoga na ye product to?
Customer: Nahi mere paas nahi hai ye dusre ke paas humko kharidna hai. Kharid kar phir customer ko dena hai.
Executive: Ek minute temporary TMPT ORA RI RY.
Customer: Haan temporary aapne kya bataya tha?
Customer: Press press maker. Press maker likhne se bhi sun aayega press P R E double S.
Executive: Aa gaya sir aa gaya.
Executive: Aapne search kiya waise apni site se IndiaMART pe?
Customer: Haan hum search search kar raha tha to number to nahi aaya ba wo koi wholesaler to abhi tak to nahi dikha.
Executive: Number nahi aata sir jo aapne jab search kiya hoga to waha pe jaise aapko profile dikhti hai to contact supplier pe aata hai na option aata hai.
Customer: Haan to aap logon ke paas to uska number hoga na jo.
Executive: Ek minute ruk jaiye sir. Aap mujhe kashmakash mein dal rahe hain ruk jaiye.
Executive: Abhi dekhta hu.
Executive: Aise rahiye search karne dijiye mujhe.
Executive: Fir sir aapko to list dikhaenge na tabhi. Hmm list to dekh len.
Executive: Ye search kiya thik hai temporary temporary pacemaker hai na?
Executive: Ye ab is is buyer ki isse na contact karna hai iska number nikalna hai. Accha ye jo hai abhi wo mobile number. Sir likhiye.
Customer: Haan kya bataiye.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan boliye bataiye.
Executive: Sir likhiye 80.
Customer: Zero.
Executive: 48.
Customer: 48.
Executive: But sir suniye suniye main aapko bata deti hu IndiaMART pe jo bhi supplier hote hai na jaise aap contact karoge inse thik hai. To ye jo number hota hai na actually ye IndiaMART ka hi diya hua hota hai actual number nahi show hota hai thik hai. To jaise maine aapko bataya na aap ek kam karo main aapko bata rahi hu aap ek kam karo google pe search karo aap abhi jo product bataya na aapne ye temporary pacemaker.
